This paper discusses the integration of LTE and mmWave technologies for 5G networks, which involves aspects of networking, information theory, multimedia, augmented reality, and system design. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.AR (Augmented Reality), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
